(192, 1, '2022-01-14 19:41:56', '2022-01-14 16:41:56', '<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">One of the main functions of RFJ tokens is the ability to combine the economies and resources of a wide variety of games and distribute them among users using the Play-to-Earn model.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Imagine you have an NFT game item in say Fifa Mobile.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-194\" src=\"https://jollity.app/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/fea534f74e243540ae12c917e1e8a242.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" /></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You use the item in the game and decide to take part in a tournament on Jollity which has 10 other games connected to it besides Fifa mobile. You have performed tasks with your in-game NFT and earned points for doing so. At the end of the tournament, you received a sum of RFJ tokens according to the points you earned. Now you can go to the marketplace and buy any in-game items you want.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">This way if you have a Fifa mobile in-game NFT item you can get any other item from other games just by playing Fifa Mobile and earning RFJ tokens. </span><span class=\"s1\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">You can build an inventory of NFT items from different games by playing just one or a few of your favorite games, and then build impressive collections and do whatever you want with them. </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">As more games get connected to Jollity the RFJ token could become a universal currency for getting, exchanging, and selling in-game items from a wide variety of games.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The same applies to the in-game currency from different games. With an RFJ token, gamers will be able to get currency from one game in the form of NFT and exchange it for currency in another.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">For example, you received NFT items that contain a certain amount of Fifa mobile coins. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-200\" src=\"https://jollity.app/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/fifa-mobile-farm-coins-guide-300x169.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"476\" height=\"268\" /></span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">By performing tasks with these NFTs (e.g. spending coins in the game), you will get RFJ tokens for the points you earn and can exchange them for in-game NFTs, which contain in themselves coins from the game Subway Surf for example. </span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-201\" src=\"https://jollity.app/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/main-qimg-90d842bccc29b1d4ff722210d1454a70-169x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"272\" height=\"483\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Our goal is for \"Reward For Joy\" tokens to become the main decentralized asset for gamers and the metaverse.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #9f25ff;\">Join us now</span>.<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\"> </span></span>', 'Why will RFJ token change the gaming industry?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'why-will-rfj-token-change-the-gaming-industry', '', '', '2022-01-14 21:06:37', '2022-01-14 18:06:37', '', 0, 'https://jollity.app/blog/?p=192', 0, 'post', '', 0),
